data.description: Nestled just outside the charming town of Mt. Shasta, this 3bd/2ba home is a true gem. As you step through the front door, you'll be immediately struck by the open and airy feel of the space, thanks to the expansive floor plan with vaulted ceilings. The large living room and family room features laminate flooring and ample natural light, making it the perfect space for relaxing or entertaining. With 3 spacious bedrooms there's plenty of room for the whole family to spread out and enjoy their own space. Outside, the .79-acre lot offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and relaxation. The backyard is a true oasis, featuring a spacious deck providing the perfect space for entertaining guests or simply enjoying the stunning natural surroundings. Home Includes a bonus room for art studio or sun room, 29x22 heavy duty metal carport with extra height for RV, plus home is wired for generator. Located just a short drive from the town of Mt. Shasta, this home offers convenient access to all the amenities this charming town has to offer, while still providing a peaceful and secluded living environment. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning property your own!
